Maybe it'’s on account of how badly I miss Eugene...

1:21:49.469 --> 1:21:51.167
but I'’ve always imagined

1:21:51.341 --> 1:21:53.473
that, for a moment,

1:21:53.647 --> 1:21:55.649
the world appeared
before him

1:21:55.823 --> 1:21:59.262
the way he always
dreamed it would.

1:21:59.436 --> 1:22:03.919
In that moment, Eugene and Allison were bound together by the dream.

1:22:06.617 --> 1:22:08.793
One they believed
they were in control of.

1:22:12.014 --> 1:22:15.931
I never been too concerned
with whose idea
the next part was.

1:22:18.281 --> 1:22:19.891
It never really
mattered much to me.

1:22:23.460 --> 1:22:27.159
There are certain conditions to the life Eugene dreamed of

1:22:27.333 --> 1:22:31.120
that I'’m sure Allison
wished she could have
kept secret from him.

1:22:34.427 --> 1:22:37.778
