Keep an eye on that watch.

1:23:02.151 --> 1:23:03.587
Kiss me.

1:23:10.333 --> 1:23:11.725
Count to five.

1:23:16.295 --> 1:23:18.994
Pardon me.
I'’m going to need that.

1:23:19.907 --> 1:23:21.083
This is a holdup!

1:23:22.562 --> 1:23:24.564
Everybody kiss the ground!

1:23:24.738 --> 1:23:27.915
Shut up! Shut up!
Get on the goddamn floor!

1:23:28.090 --> 1:23:30.396
I don'’t need you back there,
ma'’am. Get out.

1:23:30.570 --> 1:23:32.050
Everybody, calm down!You can stay.

1:23:32.224 --> 1:23:34.618
Please,
this is a family bank.

1:23:34.792 --> 1:23:36.707
I'’m not falling
for that, lady.We ain'’t insured.

1:23:36.881 --> 1:23:40.798
Everybody, calm down! Everybody!
Tell '’em! Tell '’em now!

1:23:40.972 --> 1:23:42.539
Do it.
Do as you'’re told.

1:23:42.713 --> 1:23:44.149
What now, Allison?

1:23:44.323 --> 1:23:45.629
