1:23:45.803 --> 1:23:47.283
Faster you go,
the faster we leave.

1:23:47.457 --> 1:23:50.460
Please, hear me.
We are not--Oh, I hear you.

1:23:50.634 --> 1:23:51.939
Now, hear me.

1:23:52.114 --> 1:23:53.985
I want you to open
that little safe back there.

1:23:54.159 --> 1:23:55.856
