it'’s going, lady.

1:24:00.644 --> 1:24:02.341
Good! Good!
It'’s going good!

1:24:02.515 --> 1:24:03.777
That'’s right.
Real good, kid.

1:24:03.951 --> 1:24:05.388
It'’s going well.
