1:24:09.870 --> 1:24:11.655
Thank you.
That will be all, folks.

1:24:17.530 --> 1:24:18.879
Eugene, come on.

1:24:27.497 --> 1:24:28.454
Go!

1:24:43.165 --> 1:24:46.603
Just breathe.
Come on, Eugene.
We can'’t stop.

1:24:46.777 --> 1:24:49.171
-We can'’t--
not till we get to Mexico.
- You gotta pull over.

1:24:49.345 --> 1:24:50.476
Pull over!

1:24:53.784 --> 1:24:55.699
Eugene, please.

1:24:56.830 --> 1:24:58.484
Eugene?

1:25:03.794 --> 1:25:06.188
Eugene, please,
we really gotta keep going.

1:25:09.191 --> 1:25:10.627
Kid, we gotta move.

1:25:14.500 --> 1:25:16.850
Kid, please, get in the car.

1:25:17.024 --> 1:25:19.897
One dead. Citizens Pride Bank in Stanley.

1:25:20.071 --> 1:25:24.293
Two fugitives,
including Allison Wells,
