1:25:24.467 --> 1:25:29.515
South, black truck on 281. License plate number 3285M8.

1:25:29.689 --> 1:25:31.213
I repeat--That'’s them.

1:25:32.518 --> 1:25:34.129
Goddamn!

1:25:39.090 --> 1:25:40.787
I can imagine how
you'’re feeling right now,

1:25:40.961 --> 1:25:42.833
