1:26:06.073 --> 1:26:08.598
I know.
I know how you feel.

1:26:08.772 --> 1:26:10.774
I know how you feel,
but we need to move.

1:26:10.948 --> 1:26:12.776
You need to get
in the car, Eugene.

1:26:12.950 --> 1:26:14.865
Allison, I don'’t think
