1:26:15.039 --> 1:26:16.519
I don'’t think I can do this.

1:26:16.693 --> 1:26:18.260
I do understand--You don'’t!

1:26:18.434 --> 1:26:20.044
I understand! Maybe
"I understand" doesn'’t mean

1:26:20.218 --> 1:26:22.742
I'’m just gonna sit down
and wait to die myself.

1:26:28.444 --> 1:26:29.967
How would you understand?

1:26:33.013 --> 1:26:34.276
Eugene, please.

1:26:34.450 --> 1:26:35.886
Please, get in
the goddamn car.

1:26:36.060 --> 1:26:37.409
