that I ain'’t.

1:27:11.748 --> 1:27:15.230
I didn'’t make you
into anything you didn'’t
already want to be.

1:27:21.192 --> 1:27:24.108
-Eugene.

1:27:26.980 --> 1:27:28.286
Please.

1:27:37.339 --> 1:27:38.427
Eugene!

1:27:41.865 --> 1:27:43.040
Ain'’t that your truck?

1:27:45.825 --> 1:27:47.262
Eugene!

1:27:53.180 --> 1:27:54.399
Stay here with her.

1:27:57.141 --> 1:28:00.405
Eugene, we can still
