1:29:00.770 --> 1:29:02.119
Go.

1:29:08.081 --> 1:29:10.867
If you want the bounty,
you can take me in and get it.

1:29:13.348 --> 1:29:15.175
Or we can stick to the plan.

1:29:15.350 --> 1:29:17.656
I said, get in the car.

1:29:18.440 --> 1:29:19.789
But Eugene'’s out there.

1:29:19.963 --> 1:29:22.792
I won'’t let nothing happen
to him. I promise.

1:29:22.966 --> 1:29:24.837
It'’s all right.
It'’s all right.

1:29:26.012 --> 1:29:27.100
Stay here.

